00:09:36.479 --> 00:09:38.359
But our tools are modular as well.

00:09:38.359 --> 00:09:42.200
Some teams get a lot of value out of just Connect, some like just Workbench, some like

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:45.640
just Package Manager, but they all play very nicely together.

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:51.400
And that's why we kind of offer this rounded kind of compiled offering of Positeam.

